title: 2019 Week 13 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 13 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview each of the upcoming games of week 13 while mixing in some dog references and a deep dive into the 1997 film "Titanic".
